  "summaryAcceptanceCriteria": [
    "Phase 11 is validation fixture only and performs no screenshot/OCR/browser/window access, capture, writes, network, sends, deploys, trades, or commits.",
    "Capture request records require explicit opt-in, active task scope, app/window scope, expiry, deletion policy, and James-visible controls.",
    "Allowed sources are limited to explicit active task/window/app scope or user-selected region for the active task.",
    "Always-on screen memory, background observation, all-window capture, and broad browser memory are blocked.",
    "Evidence summary records contain redacted summaries, hashes, blocked counts, and evidence refs only.",
    "Raw screenshots, OCR text, browser state, DOM, terminal scrollback, comms bodies, secrets, customer private data, and side-profile content are never exported.",
    "Privacy classes block or require review for customer private, personal private, secret/auth, side-profile, and unknown content.",
    "Raw artifacts are not retained by default and deletion-on-expiry/revoke is required.",
    "James-visible controls must show scope, allowed/blocked sources, expiry, delete, pause, revoke, and redaction summary.",
    "Perception proposal is not capture.",
    "Future capture is not a memory/profile commit.",
    "OCR or screenshot capture is not model-processing proof.",
    "Socket connection alone is not bridge green.",
    "Idempotency is stable for identical task scope and changes when task/app/window/privacy/expiry scope changes.",
    "Tests can validate fixture completeness without model calls."
